English
=======================

MP3 download here:  http://kiwi6.com/file/45r9caxbte

=======================

OK, after a couple of weeks, here comes my another new composed here.

The " Celestia garden" idea is from another image of my mind, about a magical garden in Canterlot palace,when dawn is come,trun to noon and night. different kind of fairy will came out and daning in beautiful waltz, and all kinds of flowers are blooming and release their fragrant.

just a while i was spending some time at Tamsui, the peaceful city garden of Taipei.
and the different kind of life a little bit ease my pressure, and also give me the idea of this music
this time i used the classical music form , and i consult some symphony piece of Tchaikovsky , and it's also a chance to researching more new orchestration.

this music piece take the most hard work of all "Legand of Canterlot symphony series" ,maybe it's not powerful as "the queen of blade" or "The Wrath of justice"
but i'm really doing hard on it, just hope you will love it, and i'm very appreciate about it

thank you

Sean.M

========================

中文
==========================

MP3 下載於此：  http://kiwi6.com/file/45r9caxbte

=========================

哈囉，大家，幾個禮拜過去了，新曲終於出爐了

這幾禮拜待在淡水度過假期，稍微的減緩了一些生活的壓力，同時也給了新曲的靈感，就是這首「公主的庭苑」
這感覺，就像以前在作曲「暮光森林幻想曲」的時候很像，我幻想到了Celestia公主在他宮庭後院的花園，美麗的魔法籠罩著，每當清晨、中午、入夜之時，精靈們如光點般的在空中飛舞著，如夢似幻般，而花朵也綻放著無邊的芬芳

這曲子是坎特拉傳奇中唯一使用最傳統古典音樂格式的，作這曲我特地研究了俄國作曲家柴可夫斯基的一些交響曲作品的配器法，這首曲子可以說是我作工最細的音樂，雖然說沒有如前面幾首，如「刀鋒女皇」、「怒火正義」般的充滿威力和震撼，但是論到這音樂的新穎感還有音樂的精細我是很有自信，只是一切都還是需要更多進展，而我也會繼續的求精，也希望大家能繼續支持我作品，謝謝你們，繼續支持「坎特拉傳奇交響曲系列」

親王
